<div class="tip hidden" id="tips-mfa-setup" swiping-disabled="true">
    <button class="close" onclick="hideTips(); window.location.reload();"><img src="../assets/cross.svg" alt="close" title="close mfa setup"></button>

    <div class="swiper-container" id="tips-mfa-setup-container">

        <div class="swiper-wrapper">

            <article class="swiper-slide">
                <h3 class="center">SET UP MFA</h3>
                <p class="center">scan this qr-code using your authenticator apps / devices within the next 10 minutes.</p>
                
                <div id="mfa-qr-code" class="loading"></div>
                <!-- <pre id="mfa-qr-code-secret" class="mfa-recovery-code" style="font-size: 0.75rem;"></pre> -->
                
                <button class="tips-next custom">
                    <span>next</span> 
                    <i class="ri-arrow-right-line"></i>
                </button>

            </article>

            <article class="swiper-slide">
                <h3 class="center">VERIFY MFA SETUP</h3>
                <p>enter the 6-digit mfa code generated by your authenticator app / device below:</p>
                <br>
                <input type="text" placeholder="your 6-digit mfa code" inputmode="decimal" pattern="[0-9]*" autocomplete="one-time-code" max="6" id="input-verify-mfa-code">
                <p id="mfa-verify-error" class="red"></p>
                <button class="tip-action-success" onclick="verifyMFACode()" id="button-verify-mfa">
                    <span>verify</span> 
                    <i class="ri-arrow-right-line"></i>
                </button>

            </article>

            <article class="swiper-slide" prevent-close="true">
                <h3 class="center">IMPORTANT REMINDER</h3>
                <p>on the next step, you will be presented with last-resort recovery codes to access your account if you lose access to your authenticator app / device.</p>
                <br>
                <p>as a friendly reminder, please don't write these codes into cryptee docs. we recommend using pen &amp; paper.</p>

                <button class="tips-next custom">
                    <span>i understand</span> 
                    <i class="ri-arrow-right-line"></i>
                </button>
            </article>
            
            <article class="swiper-slide" prevent-close="true">
                <h3 class="center">RECOVERY CODES</h3>
                <p style="text-align: center !important;">each code can only be used once.</p>
                <br>

                <pre class="mfa-recovery-code" id="mfa-recovery-code-1"></pre>
                <pre class="mfa-recovery-code" id="mfa-recovery-code-2"></pre>
                <pre class="mfa-recovery-code" id="mfa-recovery-code-3"></pre>
                <pre class="mfa-recovery-code" id="mfa-recovery-code-4"></pre>
                <pre class="mfa-recovery-code" id="mfa-recovery-code-5"></pre>

                <button class="tips-next custom">
                    <span>ok, i wrote them</span> 
                    <i class="ri-arrow-right-line"></i>
                </button>
            </article>

            <article class="swiper-slide">
                <h3>DONE!</h3>
                <p>Please remember to keep your last-resort recovery codes and your mfa authenticator app / device safe and private from prying eyes.</p>
            </article>

        </div>

        <!-- <div class="tips-pagination"></div> -->
        <!-- <button class="tips-next"><i class="ri-arrow-right-line"></i></button> -->

    </div>

</div>